            <lg xml:id="TK29">
<l>kuṇameṉṉuṅ kuṉṟēṟi niṉṟār vekuḷi</l>
<l>kaṇamēyuṅ kātta laritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wrath of those who have surmounted the mountain called virtue,</l>
<l>though it lasts but an instant, is hard to resist.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
